text: The 2007 Gaz de France Budapest Grand Prix was a WTA Tour tennis event held from April 21 to 29, 2007, won by Gisela Dulko. Both Dulko and Cîrstea were playing in their first final on the WTA Tour, with Dulko coming through in 3 sets. ==Singles Draw== ==Doubles Draw== ==External links== *Draws Category:Budapest Grand Prix Budapest Grand Prix Budapest Grand Prix
